Nollywood actor, Bishop Umoh, popularly known as Okon has told Nigerians to be wise and hire someone whom they can fire for the forthcoming election. Okon revealed that it would be easier to fire the Labour Party presidential candidate, Peter Obi, in an event of unlikely bad performance. Sharing a post via his Instagram account on Wednesday, he said, “Nigerians please HIRE who you can FIRE. It’s easier to fire OBI in the very unlikely event of bad performance. As for the other two, if dem enter, e Don be o! Another 8 wasted years of suffer like this one now!!! 25th is just here. Have sense!!!” 